name: Shredder
bio: Shredder is the ruthless leader of the Foot Clan. Also goes by the name Oroku Saki. Is a master of ninjustsu and psychological warfare.

name: Krang
bio: Krang is from the brain-like Utrom alien race from Dimension X. Has worked as a right-hand assistant with Shredder and the Foot Clan in the past.

name: Bebop
bio: Once a human named Anton Zeck. Now a mutant warthog. Henchman of Shredder. Often seen with Rocksteady. Strength: Brute force. Weaknesses: Low IQ.

name: Rocksteady
bio: Former human. Formerly Russian arms dealer. Former name was Ivan Steranko. Now a white rhinocerous. Henchman of Shredder. Often with Bebop. Uses high-powered weaponry.
